Package com.googlecode.prmf.merapi.net.irc.event

Events specific to the IRC protocol.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IrcEvent<C extends IncomingIrcCommand> Decorates an incoming IRC command as an event object with information about the client that received it and the entity that originated it.
IrcEventListener A listener for IRC protocol events (commands).
 

Class Summary
AbstractIrcEvent<C extends IncomingIrcCommand> A skeleton IRC event implementation.
AbstractIrcEventListener Basic implementation of the IrcEventListener interface providing empty implementations for all the methods.
